OL,7,FMore than half the public associate
OL,8,Fpoliticians with economic crime, a
OL,9,Fpoll of more than 6,000 people has
OL,10,Ffound.
OL,12,FThe poll found 54.8% of people listed
OL,13,Fpoliticians as one of the three groups
OL,14,Fthey most associated with economic
OL,15,Fcrime ` more than mentioned oligarchs
OL,16,For business executives.
