OL,5,Cpoll
OL,7,FThe findings follow years of declining
OL,8,Ftrust in politicians in general. A
OL,9,F2023 survey by King's College London's
OL,10,FPolicy Institute found trust in
OL,11,Fparliament had halved since 1990,
OL,12,Fwhile a study by the IPPR think tank
OL,13,Ffound the proportion of people who
OL,14,Fthink politicians are "merely out for
OL,15,Fthemselves" had "rapidly accelerated
OL,16,Fsince the Covid-19 pandemic".
