OL,7,F"The public think that politicians
OL,8,Fhave more to answer for than Russian
OL,9,Foligarchs and corrupt kleptocrats when
OL,10,Fit comes to dirty money in the UK.
OL,12,F"But who can blame them? These
OL,13,Ffindings follow years of ministers
OL,14,Ffailing to be tough enough on economic
OL,15,Fcrime, underinvesting in law
OL,16,Fenforcement and welcoming dirty
OL,17,FRussian money with open arms.
OL,19,F"If we want to win back the trust of
OL,20,Four constituents then we must get
OL,21,Fserious about our dirty money problem."
